data.description: For Sale or RENT! You will love this large corner lot property with an extended driveway! Bring your RV, boat, or enjoy the extra parking spaces for your guests. In the back yard you have a large deck and fenced in yard, making your space optimal for entertaining. Also located in the back yard is a small storage shed. Inside your home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, large living space with a small nook. The master bedroom is private and is the only bedroom downstairs. The bathroom boasts a gorgeous walk in shower that's floor to ceiling tile and vanity with quartz surface. Kitchen offers stainless steel appliances that all convey. Head upstairs to the additional bedrooms where you will find lots of storage and closet space.
